        <p class="card-text text-muted">His Excellency Bishop Thomas Carey joined our parish community for a solemn Mass and outdoor Eucharistic procession marking the Feast of Corpus Christi. Over 400 parishioners participated in the procession through our neighborhood streets.</p>
