        <h5 class="card-title">New RCIA Director Appointed</h5>
        <p class="card-text text-muted">We are pleased to welcome Dr. Angela Torres as our new Director of Faith Formation and RCIA. Dr. Torres brings 15 years of experience in adult faith formation from her previous role at St. Catherine's Parish.</p>
